                            "source": "Bestiary 4", 
                            "sections": [], 
                            "type": "section", 
                            "text": "<p>Natural werebats typically look like normal members of their humanoid parent race, though they often have dark hair, lithe frames, severe features, and slightly pointed ears. They typically stand taller than normal for their race, but weigh significantly less.</p>"
                        }
